<text>
  <front><div type="editorialNote"><head>Editorische Vorbemerkung</head><p>Dieser Brief ist bereits in gedruckter Form erschienen. Die bibliographischen Angaben zur Druckedition können im Metadaten-Fenster eingesehen werden.</p></div></front>
  <body>
<div type="letter">
  <pb/>
  <opener><lb/>Excellentissimi et Generosiss.<hi rend="sup">mi</hi> Domini.
  <lb/>Studiorum Mecenates Maximi.</opener>
<p><lb/>Maxima Vestra est erga me Clementia et humanitas quod me Exterum
  <lb/>in locum <abbr>Celeberr.</abbr> Doctoris <rs type="person">Guglielmini</rs> surrogare, et Splendid<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> mathe<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>matum cathedr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> in Celeberrimo vestro <rs type="organisation">Lyc<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>o Patavino</rs> me pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ficere
  <lb/>voluistis. Pro eam magnifica hac vestra erga me Benevolentia et 
  <lb/>Beneficentia gratias ago humillimas.</p><p rend="space"> Ubi hanc destinatam mihi
  <lb/>Provinciam tametsi arduam l<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tus in me suscipio, sic etiam omnes
  <lb/>meas intendam Vires ut Spartam mihi demandatam pro virili
  <lb/>exornare queam. Maximo etiam honori ducam, ut <abbr>Sereniss.<hi rend="sup">m<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></hi></abbr> <abbr>RPublic<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></abbr>
  <lb/>aut <abbr>Excell.<hi rend="sup">arum</hi></abbr> Vestrarum jussa exequendo et bonum publicum
  <lb/>quantum in me erit promovendo, meam in obediendo et voluptatem
  <lb/>et promptitudinem testatas faciam. Excellentias deni<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> Vestras
  <lb/>devotissima mente rogo, ut me deinceps honore Sui Patrocinii et
  <lb/>Protectionis afficere non dedignentur, simul<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> polliceor iter meum
  <lb/>me ingressurum esse statim ac jussa ad id Vestra scripto accepero
    <pb/>
  <lb/>quod ego hujus Urbis Civ<del>[...]</del>es; eum <abbr>Ampl.<hi rend="sup">mo</hi></abbr> nostro Magistratu communicare
  <lb/>queam. Interim nunquam esse desinam</p>
  <closer>
    <lb/>Excellentiarum Vestrarum
    <lb/>Devotissimus et humillimus
    <lb/>Servus ac Cliens
    <lb/><signed>Iacobus Hermannus</signed>
    <lb/><dateline><rs type="place">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <date when="1707-05-18">18 Maji 1707</date>.</dateline>
    <pb/>
    <address><!-- toDo: in ALMA nachtragen: Umschlag mit Siegel -->
      <addrLine>Agl' <abbr>Ecc.<hi rend="sup">mi</hi></abbr> <abbr>Sig.<hi rend="sup">ri</hi></abbr> <abbr>Sig.<hi rend="sup">ri</hi></abbr> <abbr>Pro.ni</abbr> <abbr>Col.<hi rend="sup">mi</hi></abbr></addrLine>
      <addrLine>I <abbr>Sig.<hi rend="sup">ri</hi></abbr> Riformatori dello Studio di</addrLine>
      <addrLine>Padova</addrLine>
      <addrLine>Venetia</addrLine>
    </address>
  </closer>
</div>
</body>
  
